# Target modern browsers only
# This removes unnecessary polyfills for Array.at, Object.hasOwn, etc.
# Saves ~14KB of JavaScript

# Production: Last 2 versions of modern browsers
[production]
last 2 Chrome versions
last 2 Firefox versions
last 2 Safari versions
last 2 Edge versions
not IE 11
not dead
not op_mini all

# Development: Current browser
[development]
last 1 Chrome version
last 1 Firefox version
last 1 Safari version
